Ranger Help for: rangerbug
===========================

SYNTAX:      rangerbug <message>
             rbug <message>
USAGE:       Anywhere

SUMMARY:
This command reports a bug in the Ranger guild system to the guild
maintainers. Describe the issue as clearly as possible, including
what you were doing when the bug occurred. Reports are logged for
review by the guild coders. The 'rbug' command is a shorter alias
for 'rangerbug'. Please use this for guild-specific bugs only; for
general game bugs, use the standard 'bug' command.
